## 延伸阅读 Further Reading
　  

<p style="font:bold 150% sans-serif;">礼在中国古代是社会的典章制度和道德规范<br />
Ritual, in ancient China, are laws and regulations, and ethical standards of the society</p>

<table style="width:100%;background-color:#efefef;border-collapse:collapse;">
