<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　礼在中国古代是社会的典章制度和道德规范。作为典章制度，它是社会政治制度的体现，是维护上层建筑以及与之相适应的人与人交往中的礼节仪式。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Ritual, in ancient China, are laws and regulations, and ethical standards of the society. As laws and institutions, it is a manifestation of social and political system is the maintenance of superstructure and interpersonal relationships which adapts the rituals.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">2</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　作为道德规范，它是国家领导者和贵族等一切行为的标准和要求。在孔子以前已有夏礼、殷礼、周礼。夏、殷、周三代之礼，因革相沿，到周公时代的周礼，已比较完善。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　As a code of ethics, which is the standard and requirements of national leaders and nobility and all behavior. In the summer there before Confucius ceremony, Yin Li, Zhou. Xia, Yin and Zhou Dynasties of the ceremony, Inheritance and Innovation bent along to Duke Zhou era, have been more perfect.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">3</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　作为观念形态的礼，在孔子的思想体系中是同“仁”分不开的。孔子说：“人而不仁，如礼何？”他主张“道之以德，齐之以礼”的德治，打破了“礼不下庶人”的限制。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　As ideology, Ritual, Confucius ideology is the same "benevolence" inseparable. Confucius said: "People without benevolence, such as Ritual what?" He argued, "Road to Germany, together with propriety" of virtue, breaking "ceremony less than common people" restrictions.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">4</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　到了战国时期，孟子把仁、义、礼、智作为基本的道德规范，礼为“辞让之心”，成为人的德行之一。荀子比孟子更为重视礼，他著有《礼论》，论证了“礼”的起源和社会作用。他认为礼使社会上每个人在贵贱、长幼、贫富等等级制中都有恰当的地位。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　To the Warring States period, Mencius benevolence, righteousness, propriety, wisdom as a basic ethical Ritual as "politely refuse Hearts" has become one of the human virtues. Zi Mencius more attention than the Ritual, he wrote "Ritual" theory, demonstrated that the "gift" of the origin and role in society. He believes Ritual so that everyone in the community in the poor, young and old, rich and poor, etc. have a proper hierarchy of status.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">5</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　在长期的历史发展中，礼作为中国社会的道德规范和生活准则，对中华民族精神素质的修养起了重要作用；同时，随着社会的变革和发展，礼不断被赋予新的内容，不断地发生着改变和调整。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　In the long historical development, the Ritual as the ethics and standards of living of Chinese society, the spirit of the Chinese nation and the quality of training played an important role; same time, as social change and development, Eli constantly being given new content, constantly undergoing changes and adjustments.

</td></tr>
